{"tid":1745820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有連仔一齊出post : 1124 星期日 投票","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T08:44:09.000Z","uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"572d1615d05f4d0779e38fa7babe9dae2c9c945e","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"[size=6]<br />\n全部連仔由今日起，日夜出post 到星期日晚，<br />\n務求一打開連登所有Post 都要見到叫人出嚟投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要令全部五毛收皮，不分化<br />\n仲之唔投保皇黨，唔投白票<br />\n贏左星期日呢場仗先</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJcx1Nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJcx1Nv.jpg&h=70d986c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4e0e822b733f78aea345281f3ea9d9dc09667af","tid":1745820,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"仲未明政府咩玩法既人留意<br />\n<br />\n你200萬+1人上街，佢屈9你20萬人<br />\n你5個月黎示威，佢屈你一少撮人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你只能夠講你計唔準，但佢可以話你都唔準，口同鼻拗</span><br />\n但係今次區選當公投，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係實打實既數字</span><br />\n＜就算對方種票，佢都要有身份證，影響既只會係<span style=\"color: red;\">地區議席分布，而唔係黃藍人數</span>＞<br />\n440幾萬選民，唔可能變500萬張選票<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">宜家應該係煲大區選</span><br />\n   投建制派=支持止暴制亂<br />\n   投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n結果一出黎<br />\n黃票多過200萬，政府<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以再講一少撮人</span><br />\n藍票低過200萬，<span style=\"color: red;\">輪到我地屈佢一少撮人</span><br />\n<br />\n宜家係要煲大佢<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">   投建制派=支持止暴制亂 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">  投黃投獨立=沒有暴動，只有暴政</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">選舉人數輸左=玻璃球打爛左</span><br />\n打爛左個玻璃球既後果係<br />\n1：運動失敗，逃亡潮開始<br />\n2：勇武轉化革命份子，引發更大暴力<br />\n3：香港政府管治失敗<br />\n<br />\n如果無更大暴力事件，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你都輸得甘心命抵啦，仲唔快手著草</span><br />\n輸唔起就係你起革命，唔係逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n咪發傻阻礙區選，比個位政府入<br />\n話你地一少撮人唔願意面對現實<br />\n<br />\n如果區選人頭黃多過藍，你仲可以反口話政府唔願面對現實，實實在在既數字啊<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n目標唔係含投<br />\n係要打倒建制派，無黃議員都要推假獨立<br />\n刷低對方明面上議席，清除舊有垃圾<br />\n新垃圾到時先諗計清，推到班假獨立起碼對方可以做25仔/牆頭草，唔係宜家一面倒垃圾建制派<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔覺得係公投，對家都會煲大佢變公投<br />\n先發制人<br />\n咁樣先可以動員更多港豬<br />\n<br />\n我幾個上年紀既同事仲發傻諗住唔投票<br />\n要同佢講對家會當今次係公投，先on99夢醒<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n無證無據話對方做假，大陸吹一堆假消息已經玩爛個真相<br />\n<br />\n中共外國超多打手玩假英文消息<br />\n<br />\n你要證明一件事有問題，就係要你舉出證據<br />\n否則只會當你自欺欺人<br />\n雖然信你既人會好多，但係外國佬無辦法直接插手，無證據點放上枱啊<br />\n<br />\n你今次煲大佢，<br />\n一係對方唔做手腳<br />\n黃票真係多，我地贏<br />\n<br />\n一係對方做手腳<br />\n我地/外國捉到對方做手腳，我地都贏<br />\n<br />\n捉唔到對方做手腳，就到時做文宣講選舉有問題啦<br />\n結果都係返到去，無證據，對方信定唔信<br />\n<br />\n點玩都咁被動，點解唔認真d投票"},{"pid":"a42d5ca038d6bc8cc3b67a3a3782c433c7b94077","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hx1KSWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhx1KSWy.jpg&h=8727f5a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb17816c778656c6ba4b714d54d18803d19824e4","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZD0oo3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZD0oo3j.jpg&h=7cc81580&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bde1b349e760cf6b9a319c2989202062e757e05","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DahRxWN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDahRxWN.jpg&h=1ff888f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a86cafa00686cbd69da2ced70db6647857e1366","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507a0bba0f0aba32ac7ec368b9c0480daaa6ce5d","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30282ae6ce9f80ef7ae83d71d17d692c89e0b5e","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe3fd6862dacd0676f34d23f7684176b520a2d2","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f0fe3c5eb396940c2c3d8ca50826f9bb874460","tid":1745820,"uid":321663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}